    </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;artifactId&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">spring-data-jpa</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/dependency&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;dependencies&gt;</span></code></pre>
                        </div>
