                  <div class="sect2" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                    <h3 id="core.domain-events" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.6875em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                      4.7. Publishing events from aggregate roots</h3>
                    <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                        Entities managed by repositories are aggregate roots. In a Domain-Driven Design application, these aggregate roots usually publish domain events. Spring Data provides an annotation&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@DomainEvents</code>&nbsp;you can use on a method of your aggregate root to make that publication as easy as possible.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                        Example 31. Exposing domain events from an aggregate root</div>
                      <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                        <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
										<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">class</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">AnAggregateRoot</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

    </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@DomainEvents</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Collection</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Object</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> domainEvents</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">()</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
        </span><span class="com" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 0, 0);">// … return events you want to get published here</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

    </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@AfterDomainEventsPublication</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">void</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> callbackMethod</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">()</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
       </span><span class="com" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 0, 0);">// … potentially clean up domain events list</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="colist arabic" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: -0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; background: none;">
                            <tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                            <tr style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none;">
                              <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.75em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1;">
                                &nbsp;</td>
                              <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.25em 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6;">
                                The method using&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@DomainEvents</code>&nbsp;can either return a single event instance or a collection of events. It must not take any arguments.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none;">
                              <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.75em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1;">
                                &nbsp;</td>
                              <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.25em 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6;">
                                After all events have been published, a method annotated with&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@AfterDomainEventsPublication</code>. It e.g. can be used to potentially clean the list of events to be published.</td>
                            </tr>
                            </tbody>
                          </table>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                        The methods will be called every time one of a Spring Data repository’s&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">save(…)</code>&nbsp;methods is called.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="sect2" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                    <h3 id="core.extensions" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.6875em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                      4.8. Spring Data extensions</h3>
                    <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                        This section documents a set of Spring Data extensions that enable Spring Data usage in a variety of contexts. Currently most of the integration is targeted towards Spring MVC.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sect3" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <h4 id="core.extensions.querydsl" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.4375em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                        4.8.1. Querydsl Extension - 완전히 동적으로 SQL query 를 Java 객체에서 만들어서 넘기는 방법</h4>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          <a href="http://www.querydsl.com/" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); line-height: inherit; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Querydsl</a>&nbsp;is a framework which enables the construction of statically typed SQL-like queries via its fluent API.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          Several Spring Data modules offer integration with Querydsl via&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">QueryDslPredicateExecutor</code>.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 32. QueryDslPredicateExecutor interface</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">interface</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">QueryDslPredicateExecutor</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">T</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

    T findOne</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Predicate</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> predicate</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">             </span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

    </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Iterable</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">T</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> findAll</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Predicate</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> predicate</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">   </span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

    </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">long</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> count</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Predicate</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> predicate</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">            </span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

    </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">boolean</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> exists</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Predicate</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> predicate</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">        </span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

    </span><span class="com" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 0, 0);">// … more functionality omitted.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="colist arabic" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: -0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; background: none;">
                              <tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                              <tr style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none;">
                                <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.75em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1;">
                                  &nbsp;</td>
                                <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.25em 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6;">
                                  Finds and returns a single entity matching the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Predicate</code>.</td>
                              </tr>
                              <tr style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none;">
                                <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.75em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1;">
                                  &nbsp;</td>
                                <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.25em 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6;">
                                  Finds and returns all entities matching the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Predicate</code>.</td>
                              </tr>
                              <tr style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none;">
                                <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.75em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1;">
                                  &nbsp;</td>
                                <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.25em 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6;">
                                  Returns the number of entities matching the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Predicate</code>.</td>
                              </tr>
                              <tr style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none;">
                                <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.75em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1;">
                                  &nbsp;</td>
                                <td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.25em 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6;">
                                  Returns if an entity that matches the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Predicate</code>&nbsp;exists.</td>
                              </tr>
                              </tbody>
                            </table>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          To make use of Querydsl support simply extend&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">QueryDslPredicateExecutor</code>&nbsp;on your repository interface.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 33. Querydsl integration on repositories</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">interface</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">UserRepository</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">CrudRepository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Long</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">QueryDslPredicateExecutor</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          The above enables to write typesafe queries using Querydsl&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Predicate</code>&nbsp;s.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
									<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Predicate</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> predicate </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> user</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">firstname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">equalsIgnoreCase</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"dave"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
	</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">and</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">user</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">lastname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">startsWithIgnoreCase</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"mathews"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">));</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

userRepository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">findAll</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">predicate</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span></code></pre>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sect3" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <h4 id="core.web" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.4375em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                        4.8.2. Web support</h4>
                      <div class="admonitionblock note" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; border: 0px; width: 970px; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">
                          <tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                          <tr style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                            <td class="icon" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; width: 80px;">
                              &nbsp;</td>
                            <td class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 1.25em 0.5625em 1.125em; direction: ltr; font-size: 1.0625rem; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 216);">
                              This section contains the documentation for the Spring Data web support as it is implemented as of Spring Data Commons in the 1.6 range. As it the newly introduced support changes quite a lot of things we kept the documentation of the former behavior in&nbsp;<a href="http://docs.spring.io/spring-data/jpa/docs/2.0.0.M3/reference/html/#web.legacy" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); line-height: inherit; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Legacy web support</a>.</td>
                          </tr>
                          </tbody>
                        </table>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          Spring Data modules ships with a variety of web support if the module supports the repository programming model. The web related stuff requires Spring MVC JARs on the classpath, some of them even provide integration with Spring HATEOAS&nbsp;<span class="footnote" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12.75px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;">[<a class="footnote" href="http://docs.spring.io/spring-data/jpa/docs/2.0.0.M3/reference/html/#_footnote_2" id="_footnoteref_2" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); line-height: inherit; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;" title="View footnote.">2</a>]</span>. In general, the integration support is enabled by using the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@EnableSpringDataWebSupport</code>&nbsp;annotation in your JavaConfig configuration class.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 34. Enabling Spring Data web support</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Configuration</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@EnableWebMvc</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@EnableSpringDataWebSupport</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">class</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">WebConfiguration</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          The&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@EnableSpringDataWebSupport</code>&nbsp;annotation registers a few components we will discuss in a bit. It will also detect Spring HATEOAS on the classpath and register integration components for it as well if present.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          Alternatively, if you are using XML configuration, register either&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">SpringDataWebSupport</code>&nbsp;or<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">HateoasAwareSpringDataWebSupport</code>&nbsp;as Spring beans:</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 35. Enabling Spring Data web support in XML</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;bean</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">class</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"org.springframework.data.web.config.SpringDataWebConfiguration"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">/&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

</span><span class="com" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 0, 0);">&lt;!-- If you're using Spring HATEOAS as well register this one *instead* of the former --&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;bean</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">class</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"org.springframework.data.web.config.HateoasAwareSpringDataWebConfiguration"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">/&gt;</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="sect4" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <h5 id="core.web.basic" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.125em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                          Basic web support</h5>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            The configuration setup shown above will register a few basic components:</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ulist" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em 1.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; list-style-position: outside; font-family: inherit;">
                            <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                              <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                A&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">DomainClassConverter</code>&nbsp;to enable Spring MVC to resolve instances of repository managed domain classes from request parameters or path variables.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                              <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                <code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">HandlerMethodArgumentResolver</code>&nbsp;implementations to let Spring MVC resolve Pageable and Sort instances from request parameters.</p>
                            </li>
                          </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sect5" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <h6 id="core.web.basic.domain-class-converter" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                            DomainClassConverter</h6>
                          <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              The&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">DomainClassConverter</code>&nbsp;allows you to use domain types in your Spring MVC controller method signatures directly, so that you don’t have to manually lookup the instances via the repository:</p>
                          </div>
                          <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                              Example 36. A Spring MVC controller using domain types in method signatures</div>
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                              <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                                <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
													<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Controller</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@RequestMapping</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"/users"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">class</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">UserController</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@RequestMapping</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"/{id}"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> showUserForm</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@PathVariable</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"id"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> user</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Model</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> model</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

    model</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">addAttribute</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"user"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> user</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">return</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"userForm"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              As you can see the method receives a User instance directly and no further lookup is necessary. The instance can be resolved by letting Spring MVC convert the path variable into the id type of the domain class first and eventually access the instance through calling&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">findOne(…)</code>&nbsp;on the repository instance registered for the domain type.</p>
                          </div>
                          <div class="admonitionblock note" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; border: 0px; width: 970px; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">
                              <tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                              <tr style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                                <td class="icon" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; width: 80px;">
                                  &nbsp;</td>
                                <td class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 1.25em 0.5625em 1.125em; direction: ltr; font-size: 1.0625rem; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 216);">
                                  Currently the repository has to implement&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">CrudRepository</code>&nbsp;to be eligible to be discovered for conversion.</td>
                              </tr>
                              </tbody>
                            </table>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sect5" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <h6 id="core.web.basic.paging-and-sorting" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                            HandlerMethodArgumentResolvers for Pageable and Sort</h6>
                          <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              The configuration snippet above also registers a&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PageableHandlerMethodArgumentResolver</code>&nbsp;as well as an instance of<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">SortHandlerMethodArgumentResolver</code>. The registration enables&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Pageable</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Sort</code>&nbsp;being valid controller method arguments</p>
                          </div>
                          <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                              Example 37. Using Pageable as controller method argument</div>
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                              <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                                <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
													<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Controller</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@RequestMapping</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"/users"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">class</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">UserController</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Autowired</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">UserRepository</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> repository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@RequestMapping</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> showUsers</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Model</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> model</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Pageable</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> pageable</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

    model</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">addAttribute</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"users"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> repository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">findAll</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">pageable</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">));</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">return</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"users"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              This method signature will cause Spring MVC try to derive a Pageable instance from the request parameters using the following default configuration:</p>
                          </div>
                          <table class="tableblock frame-all grid-all" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); max-width: 100%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
                            <caption class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.25em; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; text-align: left; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic; white-space: nowrap; overflow: visible; max-width: 0px;">
                              Table 1. Request parameters evaluated for Pageable instances</caption>
                            <colgroup style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                              <col style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                              <col style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                            </colgroup>
                            <tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                            <tr style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                              <td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border-top-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top;">
                                <p class="tableblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                  <code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background: none;">page</code></p>
                              </td>
                              <td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top;">
                                <p class="tableblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                  Page you want to retrieve, 0 indexed and defaults to 0.</p>
                              </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr style="box-sizing: border-box; background: rgb(248, 248, 247);">
                              <td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border-top-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top;">
                                <p class="tableblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                  <code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background: none;">size</code></p>
                              </td>
                              <td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top;">
                                <p class="tableblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                  Size of the page you want to retrieve, defaults to 20.</p>
                              </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                              <td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top;">
                                <p class="tableblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                  <code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background: none;">sort</code></p>
                              </td>
                              <td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border: 0px solid rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top;">
                                <p class="tableblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                  Properties that should be sorted by in the format&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">property,property(,ASC|DESC)</code>. Default sort direction is ascending. Use multiple&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">sort</code>&nbsp;parameters if you want to switch directions, e.g.&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">?sort=firstname&amp;sort=lastname,asc</code>.</p>
                              </td>
                            </tr>
                            </tbody>
                          </table>
                          <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              To customize this behavior extend either&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">SpringDataWebConfiguration</code>&nbsp;or the HATEOAS-enabled equivalent and override the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">pageableResolver()</code>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">sortResolver()</code>&nbsp;methods and import your customized configuration file instead of using the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Enable</code>-annotation.</p>
                          </div>
                          <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              In case you need multiple&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Pageable</code>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Sort</code>&nbsp;instances to be resolved from the request (for multiple tables, for example) you can use Spring’s&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Qualifier</code>&nbsp;annotation to distinguish one from another. The request parameters then have to be prefixed with&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">${qualifier}_</code>. So for a method signature like this:</p>
                          </div>
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> showUsers</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Model</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> model</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
      </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Qualifier</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"foo"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Pageable</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> first</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
      </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Qualifier</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"bar"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Pageable</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> second</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">…</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              you have to populate&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">foo_page</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">bar_page</code>&nbsp;etc.</p>
                          </div>
                          <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              The default&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Pageable</code>&nbsp;handed into the method is equivalent to a&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">new PageRequest(0, 20)</code>&nbsp;but can be customized using the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@PageableDefaults</code>&nbsp;annotation on the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Pageable</code>&nbsp;parameter.</p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="sect4" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <h5 id="core.web.pageables" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.125em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                          Hypermedia support for Pageables</h5>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            Spring HATEOAS ships with a representation model class&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PagedResources</code>&nbsp;that allows enriching the content of a&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Page</code>instance with the necessary&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Page</code>&nbsp;metadata as well as links to let the clients easily navigate the pages. The conversion of a Page to a&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PagedResources</code>&nbsp;is done by an implementation of the Spring HATEOAS&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">ResourceAssembler</code>&nbsp;interface, the<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PagedResourcesAssembler</code>.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                            Example 38. Using a PagedResourcesAssembler as controller method argument</div>
                          <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                            <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                              <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
												<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Controller</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
