                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            Enabling the configuration as shown above allows the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PagedResourcesAssembler</code>&nbsp;to be used as controller method argument. Calling&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">toResources(…)</code>&nbsp;on it will cause the following:</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ulist" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em 1.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; list-style-position: outside; font-family: inherit;">
                            <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                              <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                The content of the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Page</code>&nbsp;will become the content of the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PagedResources</code>&nbsp;instance.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                              <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                The&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PagedResources</code>&nbsp;will get a&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PageMetadata</code>&nbsp;instance attached populated with information form the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Page</code>&nbsp;and the underlying&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PageRequest</code>.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                              <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                The&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PagedResources</code>&nbsp;gets&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">prev</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">next</code>&nbsp;links attached depending on the page’s state. The links will point to the URI the method invoked is mapped to. The pagination parameters added to the method will match the setup of the<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">PageableHandlerMethodArgumentResolver</code>&nbsp;to make sure the links can be resolved later on.</p>
                            </li>
                          </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            Assume we have 30 Person instances in the database. You can now trigger a request&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">GET<a class="bare" href="http://localhost:8080/persons" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); line-height: inherit; background: transparent;">http://localhost:8080/persons</a></code>&nbsp;and you’ll see something similar to this:</p>
