  </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;property</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">name</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"webBindingInitializer"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;bean</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">class</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"….web.bind.support.ConfigurableWebBindingInitializer"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
      </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;property</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">name</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"propertyEditorRegistrars"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
        </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;bean</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">class</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"org.springframework.data.repository.support.DomainClassPropertyEditorRegistrar"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">/&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
      </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/property&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/bean&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/property&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/bean&gt;</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              If you have configured Spring MVC as in the preceding example, you can configure your controller as follows, which reduces a lot of the clutter and boilerplate.</p>
