                    <div class="sect3" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <h4 id="jpa.named-parameters" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.4375em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                        5.3.6. Using named parameters</h4>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          By default Spring Data JPA will use position based parameter binding as described in all the samples above. This makes query methods a little error prone to refactoring regarding the parameter position. To solve this issue you can use<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Param</code>&nbsp;annotation to give a method parameter a concrete name and bind the name in the query.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 53. Using named parameters - 네임드 파라미터를 주면, ?1, ?2 등으로 파라미터 순서를 기억하지 않아도 되므로 파라미터 순서에 유연해진다.</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">interface</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">UserRepository</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">JpaRepository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Long</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Query</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"select u from User u where u.firstname = :firstname or u.lastname = :lastname"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> findByLastnameOrFirstname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Param</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"lastname"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> lastname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
                                 </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Param</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"firstname"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> firstname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          Note that the method parameters are switched according to the occurrence in the query defined.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="admonitionblock note" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; border: 0px; width: 970px; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">
                          <tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                          <tr style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                            <td class="icon" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; width: 80px;">
                              &nbsp;</td>
                            <td class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 1.25em 0.5625em 1.125em; direction: ltr; font-size: 1.0625rem; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 216);">
                              <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                  Spring 4 fully supports Java 8’s parameter name discovery based on the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">-parameters</code>&nbsp;compiler flag. Using this flag in your build as an alternative to debug information, you can omit the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Param</code>&nbsp;annotation for named parameters.</p>
                              </div>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                          </tbody>
                        </table>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sect3" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <h4 id="jpa.query.spel-expressions" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.4375em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                        5.3.7. Using SpEL expressions - 동적인 쿼리문의 유연성을 줄때, 쿼리에 템플릿 기능을 제공한다. #{...} 식으로 넣는다.</h4>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          As of Spring Data JPA release 1.4 we support the usage of restricted SpEL template expressions in manually defined queries via&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Query</code>. Upon query execution these expressions are evaluated against a predefined set of variables. We support the following list of variables to be used in a manual query.</p>
                      </div>
                      <table class="tableblock frame-all grid-all" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); max-width: 100%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
                        <caption class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.25em; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; text-align: left; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic; white-space: nowrap; overflow: visible; max-width: 0px;">
                          Table 5. Supported variables inside SpEL based query templates</caption>
                        <colgroup style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                          <col style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                          <col style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                          <col style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                        </colgroup>
                        <thead style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; background: rgb(247, 248, 247);">
                        <tr style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                          <th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0.625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border-top-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;">
                            Variable</th>
                          <th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0.625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border-top-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;">
                            Usage</th>
                          <th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0.625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;">
                            Description</th>
                        </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                        <tr style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                          <td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top;">
                            <p class="tableblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              <code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background: none;">entityName</code></p>
                          </td>
                          <td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top;">
                            <p class="tableblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              <code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background: none;">select x from #{#entityName} x</code></p>
                          </td>
                          <td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; border: 0px solid rgb(222, 222, 222); vertical-align: top;">
                            <p class="tableblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                              Inserts the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">entityName</code>&nbsp;of the domain type associated with the given Repository. The<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">entityName</code>&nbsp;is resolved as follows: If the domain type has set the name property on the<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Entity</code>&nbsp;annotation then it will be used. Otherwise the simple class-name of the domain type will be used.</p>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                        </tbody>
                      </table>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          The following example demonstrates one use case for the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">#{#entityName}</code>&nbsp;expression in a query string where you want to define a repository interface with a query method with a manually defined query. In order not to have to state the actual entity name in the query string of a&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Query</code>&nbsp;annotation one can use the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">#{#entityName}</code>&nbsp;Variable.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="admonitionblock note" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; border: 0px; width: 970px; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">
                          <tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                          <tr style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                            <td class="icon" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; width: 80px;">
                              &nbsp;</td>
                            <td class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 1.25em 0.5625em 1.125em; direction: ltr; font-size: 1.0625rem; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 216);">
                              <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                  The&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">entityName</code>&nbsp;can be customized via the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Entity</code>&nbsp;annotation. Customizations via&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">orm.xml</code>&nbsp;are not supported for the SpEL expressions.</p>
                              </div>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                          </tbody>
                        </table>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 54. Using SpEL expressions in repository query methods - entityName</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Entity</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">class</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Id</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@GeneratedValue</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Long</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> id</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> lastname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">interface</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">UserRepository</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">JpaRepository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Long</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Query</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"select u from #{#entityName} u where u.lastname = ?1"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">List</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> findByLastname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> lastname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          Of course you could have just used User in the query declaration directly but that would require you to change the query as well. The reference to&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">#entityName</code>&nbsp;will pick up potential future remappings of the User class to a different entity name (e.g. by using&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Entity(name = "MyUser")</code>.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          Another use case for the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">#{#entityName}</code>&nbsp;expression in a query string is if you want to define a generic repository interface with specialized repository interfaces for a concrete domain type. In order not to have to repeat the definition of custom query methods on the concrete interfaces you can use the entity name expression in the query string of the<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Query</code>&nbsp;annotation in the generic repository interface.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 55. Using SpEL expressions in repository query methods - entityName with inheritance</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@MappedSuperclass</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
