  </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">…</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> attribute
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

</span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Entity</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">class</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">ConcreteType</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">AbstractMappedType</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">…</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

</span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@NoRepositoryBean</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">interface</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">MappedTypeRepository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">T </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">AbstractMappedType</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Repository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">T</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Long</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Query</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"select t from #{#entityName} t where t.attribute = ?1"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">List</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">T</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> findAllByAttribute</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> attribute</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">interface</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">ConcreteRepository</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">MappedTypeRepository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">ConcreteType</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">…</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          In the example the interface&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">MappedTypeRepository</code>&nbsp;is the common parent interface for a few domain types extending<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">AbstractMappedType</code>. It also defines the generic method&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">findAllByAttribute(…)</code>&nbsp;which can be used on instances of the specialized repository interfaces. If you now invoke&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">findByAllAttribute(…)</code>&nbsp;on&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">ConcreteRepository</code>&nbsp;the query being executed will be&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">select t from ConcreteType t where t.attribute = ?1</code>.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sect3" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <h4 id="jpa.modifying-queries" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.4375em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                        5.3.8. Modifying queries - Update 와 delete 등의 쿼리에는 @Modifying 이라고 선언해준다.</h4>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          All the sections above describe how to declare queries to access a given entity or collection of entities. Of course you can add custom modifying behaviour by using facilities described in&nbsp;<a href="http://docs.spring.io/spring-data/jpa/docs/2.0.0.M3/reference/html/#repositories.custom-implementations" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); line-height: inherit; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Custom implementations for Spring Data repositories</a>. As this approach is feasible for comprehensive custom functionality, you can achieve the execution of modifying queries that actually only need parameter binding by annotating the query method with&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Modifying</code>:</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 56. Declaring manipulating queries</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Modifying</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Query</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"update User u set u.firstname = ?1 where u.lastname = ?2"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">int</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> setFixedFirstnameFor</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> firstname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> lastname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          This will trigger the query annotated to the method as updating query instead of a selecting one. As the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">EntityManager</code>might contain outdated entities after the execution of the modifying query, we do not automatically clear it (see JavaDoc of&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">EntityManager.clear()</code>&nbsp;for details) since this will effectively drop all non-flushed changes still pending in the<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">EntityManager</code>. If you wish the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">EntityManager</code>&nbsp;to be cleared automatically you can set&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Modifying</code>&nbsp;annotation’s<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">clearAutomatically</code>&nbsp;attribute to&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">true</code>.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="sect4" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <h5 id="jpa.modifying-queries.derived-delete" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.125em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                          Derived delete queries</h5>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            Spring Data JPA also supports derived delete queries that allow you to avoid having to declare the JPQL query explicitly.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                            Example 57. Using a derived delete query</div>
                          <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                            <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                              <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
												<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">interface</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">UserRepository</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Repository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Long</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">void</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> deleteByRoleId</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">long</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> roleId</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Modifying</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Query</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"delete from User u where user.role.id = ?1"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">void</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> deleteInBulkByRoleId</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">long</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> roleId</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            Although the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">deleteByRoleId(…)</code>&nbsp;method looks like it’s basically producing the same result as the<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">deleteInBulkByRoleId(…)</code>, there is an important difference between the two method declarations in terms of the way they get executed. As the name suggests, the latter method will issue a single JPQL query (i.e. the one defined in the annotation) against the database. This means, even currently loaded instances of&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">User</code>&nbsp;won’t see lifecycle callbacks invoked.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            To make sure lifecycle queries are actually invoked, an invocation of&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">deleteByRoleId(…)</code>&nbsp;will actually execute a query and then deleting the returned instances one by one, so that the persistence provider can actually invoke&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@PreRemove</code>callbacks on those entities.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            In fact, a derived delete query is a shortcut for executing the query and then calling<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">CrudRepository.delete(Iterable&lt;User&gt; users)</code>&nbsp;on the result and keep behavior in sync with the implementations of other&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">delete(…)</code>&nbsp;methods in&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">CrudRepository</code>.</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sect3" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <h4 id="jpa.query-hints" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.4375em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                        5.3.9. Applying query hints</h4>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          To apply JPA query hints to the queries declared in your repository interface you can use the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@QueryHints</code>&nbsp;annotation. It takes an array of JPA&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@QueryHint</code>&nbsp;annotations plus a boolean flag to potentially disable the hints applied to the addtional count query triggered when applying pagination.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 58. Using QueryHints with a repository method</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">interface</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">UserRepository</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Repository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Long</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@QueryHints</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">value </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@QueryHint</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">name </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"name"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> value </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="str" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"value"</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)},</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
              forCounting </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">false</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Page</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> findByLastname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> lastname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Pageable</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> pageable</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          The just shown declaration would apply the configured&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@QueryHint</code>&nbsp;for that actually query but omit applying it to the count query triggered to calculate the total number of pages.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sect3" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <h4 id="jpa.entity-graph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.4375em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                        5.3.10. Configuring Fetch- and LoadGraphs - 조인으로 참조하는 객체의 프로퍼티를 select a.detail, b.* from a, b where a.id=b.id 라고 가정하면, 해당 detail 을&nbsp;</h4>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          The JPA 2.1 specification introduced support for specifiying Fetch- and LoadGraphs that we also support via the<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@EntityGraph</code>&nbsp;annotation which allows to reference a&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@NamedEntityGraph</code>&nbsp;definition, that can be annotated on an entity, to be used to configure the fetch plan of the resulting query. The type (Fetch / Load) of the fetching can be configured via the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">type</code>&nbsp;attribute on the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@EntityGraph</code>&nbsp;annotation. Please have a look at the JPA 2.1 Spec 3.7.4 for further reference.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 59. Defining a named entity graph on an entity.</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
