										<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">interface</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">UserRepository</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Repository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Long</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="com" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 0, 0);">// Plain query method</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Lock</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">LockModeType</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">READ</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">List</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> findByLastname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">String</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> lastname</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                        This method declaration will cause the query being triggered to be equipped with the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">LockModeType</code>&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">READ</code>. You can also define locking for CRUD methods by redeclaring them in your repository interface and adding the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@Lock</code>&nbsp;annotation:</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                        Example 84. Defining lock metadata on CRUD methods</div>
                      <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                        <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
										<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">interface</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">UserRepository</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">extends</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Repository</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">,</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Long</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="com" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 0, 0);">// Redeclaration of a CRUD method</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@Lock</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">LockModeType</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">.</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">READ</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">List</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> findAll</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">();</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="sect2" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                    <h3 id="auditing" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.6875em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                      5.9. Auditing</h3>
                    <div class="sect3" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <h4 id="auditing.basics" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.4375em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                        5.9.1. Basics</h4>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          Spring Data provides sophisticated support to transparently keep track of who created or changed an entity and the point in time this happened. To benefit from that functionality you have to equip your entity classes with auditing metadata that can be defined either using annotations or by implementing an interface.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="sect4" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <h5 id="auditing.annotations" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.125em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                          Annotation based auditing metadata</h5>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            We provide&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@CreatedBy</code>,&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@LastModifiedBy</code>&nbsp;to capture the user who created or modified the entity as well as<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@CreatedDate</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@LastModifiedDate</code>&nbsp;to capture the point in time this happened.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                            Example 85. An audited entity</div>
                          <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                            <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                              <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
												<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">class</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">Customer</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@CreatedBy</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">private</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> user</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="lit" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 102, 102);">@CreatedDate</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">private</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">DateTime</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> createdDate</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="com" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 0, 0);">// … further properties omitted</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></code></pre>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            As you can see, the annotations can be applied selectively, depending on which information you’d like to capture. For the annotations capturing the points in time can be used on properties of type JodaTimes&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">DateTime</code>, legacy Java&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Date</code>&nbsp;and<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Calendar</code>, JDK8 date/time types as well as&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">long</code>/<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Long</code>.</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="sect4" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <h5 id="auditing.interfaces" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.125em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                          Interface-based auditing metadata</h5>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            In case you don’t want to use annotations to define auditing metadata you can let your domain class implement the<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Auditable</code>&nbsp;interface. It exposes setter methods for all of the auditing properties.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            There’s also a convenience base class&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">AbstractAuditable</code>&nbsp;which you can extend to avoid the need to manually implement the interface methods. Be aware that this increases the coupling of your domain classes to Spring Data which might be something you want to avoid. Usually the annotation based way of defining auditing metadata is preferred as it is less invasive and more flexible.</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="sect4" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <h5 id="auditing.auditor-aware" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.125em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                          AuditorAware</h5>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            In case you use either&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@CreatedBy</code>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@LastModifiedBy</code>, the auditing infrastructure somehow needs to become aware of the current principal. To do so, we provide an&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">AuditorAware&lt;T&gt;</code>&nbsp;SPI interface that you have to implement to tell the infrastructure who the current user or system interacting with the application is. The generic type&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">T</code>&nbsp;defines of what type the properties annotated with&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@CreatedBy</code>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">@LastModifiedBy</code>&nbsp;have to be.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            Here’s an example implementation of the interface using Spring Security’s&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">Authentication</code>&nbsp;object:</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                            Example 86. Implementation of AuditorAware based on Spring Security</div>
                          <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                            <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                              <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
												<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">class</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">SpringSecurityAuditorAware</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">implements</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">AuditorAware</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

  </span><span class="kwd" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">public</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="typ" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">User</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> getCurrentAuditor</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">()</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">{</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

