                    <div class="sect3" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <h4 id="jpa.misc.entity-scanning" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.4375em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                        6.2.1. Classpath scanning for @Entity classes and JPA mapping files</h4>
                      <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                          A plain JPA setup requires all annotation mapped entity classes listed in&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">orm.xml</code>. Same applies to XML mapping files. Spring Data JPA provides a ClasspathScanningPersistenceUnitPostProcessor that gets a base package configured and optionally takes a mapping filename pattern. It will then scan the given package for classes annotated with @Entity or @MappedSuperclass and also loads the configuration files matching the filename pattern and hands them to the JPA configuration. The PostProcessor has to be configured like this:</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                          Example 92. Using ClasspathScanningPersistenceUnitPostProcessor</div>
                        <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;bean</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">class</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"….LocalContainerEntityManagerFactoryBean"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;property</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">name</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"persistenceUnitPostProcessors"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;list&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
      </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;bean</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">class</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"org.springframework.data.jpa.support.ClasspathScanningPersistenceUnitPostProcessor"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
        </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;constructor-arg</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">value</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"com.acme.domain"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">/&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
        </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;property</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">name</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"mappingFileNamePattern"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">value</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"**/*Mapping.xml"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">/&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
      </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/bean&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/list&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/property&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/bean&gt;</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="admonitionblock note" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                        <table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; border: 0px; width: 970px; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">
                          <tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                          <tr style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                            <td class="icon" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 0.625em; direction: ltr; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; width: 80px;">
                              &nbsp;</td>
                            <td class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5625em 1.25em 0.5625em 1.125em; direction: ltr; font-size: 1.0625rem; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 216);">
                              <div class="paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                                  As of Spring 3.1 a package to scan can be configured on the LocalContainerEntityManagerFactoryBean directly to enable classpath scanning for entity classes. See the&nbsp;<a href="http://docs.spring.io/spring/docs/current/javadoc-api/org/springframework/orm/jpa/LocalContainerEntityManagerFactoryBean.html#setPackagesToScan(java.lang.String...)" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); line-height: inherit; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">JavaDoc</a>&nbsp;for details.</p>
