              <div class="sect1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.25em; direction: ltr; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(239, 239, 237);">
                <h2 id="faq" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 2.3125em; word-spacing: -0.05em; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                  Appendix E: Frequently asked questions</h2>
                <div class="sectionbody" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                  <div class="sect2" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                    <h3 id="_common" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.6875em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                      Common</h3>
                    <div class="qlist qanda" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em 1.75em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; list-style-position: outside; font-family: inherit;">
                        <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            <em style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;">I’d like to get more detailed logging information on what methods are called inside&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; font-style: normal !important; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">JpaRepository</code>, e.g. How can I gain them?</em></p>
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            You can make use of&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">CustomizableTraceInterceptor</code>&nbsp;provided by Spring:</p>
                          <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
											<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;bean</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">id</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"customizableTraceInterceptor"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">class</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"
  org.springframework.aop.interceptor.CustomizableTraceInterceptor"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;property</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">name</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"enterMessage"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">value</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"Entering $[methodName]($[arguments])"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">/&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;property</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">name</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"exitMessage"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">value</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"Leaving $[methodName](): $[returnValue]"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">/&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/bean&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">

</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;aop:config&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;aop:advisor</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">advice-ref</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"customizableTraceInterceptor"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
    </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">pointcut</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"execution(public * org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository+.*(..))"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">/&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/aop:config&gt;</span></code></pre>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </li>
                      </ol>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="sect2" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                    <h3 id="_infrastructure" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.6875em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                      Infrastructure</h3>
                    <div class="qlist qanda" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em 1.75em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; list-style-position: outside; font-family: inherit;">
                        <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            <em style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;">Currently I have implemented a repository layer based on&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; font-style: normal !important; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">HibernateDaoSupport</code>. I create a&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; font-style: normal !important; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">SessionFactory</code>&nbsp;by using Spring’s&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; font-style: normal !important; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">AnnotationSessionFactoryBean</code>. How do I get Spring Data repositories working in this environment?</em></p>
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            You have to replace&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">AnnotationSessionFactoryBean</code>&nbsp;with the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">HibernateJpaSessionFactoryBean</code>&nbsp;as follows:</p>
                          <div class="exampleblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                            <div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                              Example 93. Looking up a SessionFactory from a HibernateEntityManagerFactory</div>
                            <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; padding: 1.25em; direction: ltr; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 220); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(224, 224, 220) 0px 1px 4px; background: rgb(255, 254, 247);">
                              <div class="listingblock" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                                <div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative;">
													<pre class="prettyprint highlight prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.90625em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1em; direction: ltr; line-height: 1.45; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px solid rgb(136, 136, 136); background: rgb(247, 247, 248);"><code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;"><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;bean</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">id</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"sessionFactory"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">class</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"org.springframework.orm.jpa.vendor.HibernateJpaSessionFactoryBean"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
  </span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;property</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">name</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"entityManagerFactory"</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span><span class="atn" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 0, 102);">ref</span><span class="pun" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="atv" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">"entityManagerFactory"</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">/&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
</span><span class="tag" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">&lt;/bean&gt;</span></code></pre>
