                  <div class="sect2" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                    <h3 id="_auditing" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(0, 136, 0); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.6875em; word-spacing: -0.05em;">
                      Auditing</h3>
                    <div class="qlist qanda" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                      <ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25em 1.75em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.6; list-style-position: outside; font-family: inherit;">
                        <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; direction: ltr;">
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            <em style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;">I want to use Spring Data JPA auditing capabilities but have my database already set up to set modification and creation date on entities. How to prevent Spring Data from setting the date programmatically.</em></p>
                          <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
                            Just use the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">set-dates</code>&nbsp;attribute of the&nbsp;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9375em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.5ex; word-spacing: -0.15em; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.45; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);">auditing</code>&nbsp;namespace element to false.</p>
                        </li>
                      </ol>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="sect1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.25em; direction: ltr; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(239, 239, 237);">
